So, potential difference across $6 \mu \mathrm{F}$ is 6 V .
Hence $\mathrm{Q}=\mathrm{C} \Delta \mathrm{V}$

$$ 
\begin{aligned}
& =6 \times 6 \times 10^{-6} \mathrm{C} \\
